                        <div class="slide__text">
                            <h2 class="slide__text-heading">Living Root Bridge</h2>
                            <p class="slide__text-desc">The southern Khasi and Jaintia hills are humid and warm, crisscrossed by swift-flowing rivers and mountain streams. On the slopes of these hills, a species of Indian rubber tree with an incredibly strong root system thrives and flourishes.</p>
                             <h6>Photo by Abhas Mishra </h6>
